						<td>
						<p ALIGN="LEFT" class="subtitle">Sauer &amp; Steiner 
						Toolworks
						<font size="2">
						<span style="font-weight: 400">by Christopher 
				Schwarz<br>
						</span></font>
						<font style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 400">Copyright 
						2006. This article originally appeared in the
						<a target="_blank" href="../../../0_track/cs_FineToolJourn-track.asp">Fine 
